      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "FUN EFFECTS (7) has been hard to follow lately, running fifth (17.95) last time but prior to that ran very well when placed at this track. Can turn form around here. SEE RED (4) ran good time (17.53) when placing two back at this track but missed the frame latest in a Grade 5 at this track. This looks easier and expected to improve sharply. REEL'EM CHAPPO (3) continues to race well but is struggling to break through, placing at his last four runs. Last time finished 3rd on January 3 over 300m at this track behind Keylin beaten 0.8 lengths (17.66) in a Grade 4. The form out of the last run is proven to be strong. Nicely placed to grab a well-deserved win. WHAT A SECRET (6) picked up a cheque last time and is in the mix again.",
